Swim Team

$
The program requires the participant to be a member of the Y.  The program is for ages 7 and up, even adult triathletes swim with the team,  Parents/participants pay the Swim team coach directly, All participants must be able to swim the the length of the pool Freestyle and return the length of the pool with Backstroke.

Leadership Team
/$
/$
$
$
$
$
The Highlands County YMCA is committed to making great things happen in the lives of our members and for those in the community. Change is made possible due to the hard work and dedication of our YMCA staff members. Our Leadership Team is comprised of
individuals who pledge their time and energy to furthering the goals and ideals of the Highlands County YMCA.
We welcome you to stop by and say hello!

Board of Directors
/$
/$
$
$
$
$
Board members are
community leaders and role models who are dedicated to the YMCA’s mission to build strong kids, families and communities.
The YMCA owes much of its success to these board members who have brought knowledge, compassion and a desire to further the goals of the YMCA to our members and the community. We are thankful to these individuals for donating their time and efforts to ensure that we are reaching our fullest potential!
